}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "F5U234-C REV:1.2 /1.6mm" and the '''Belkin''' logo is silkscreened on the board. :The '''Cypress''' hub IC is marked with "CY7C65640-", LFXC 0505", "D 04", "CYP 604275", "KOR []". :The device is using all '''Canicon''' capacitors and a '''NSK''' 24.000MHz oscillator.
This device is presumed to be a v1 unit (are there even other revisions?). There is no revision/version information on the device's label (molded into the plastic). :The S/N on this unit is worn off..
The power adapter included with the unit ''may'' be a '''Fairway Electronic''' WN10A-050U (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz -> 5VDC 2.5A).
